Colour in life
. Body and pereopods generally orange; carapace with 4 transverse, white bands; each pleonite with 1 white transverse band; pleopods, telson and uropodal endopods entirely orange; uropodal exopods generally white with posterior margin orange. Cornea of eye brownish, opaque; eyestalk orange (

