The new species can be readily distinguished from 

G. keralam
Padate, Cubelio & Takeda, 2022

from the Indian Ocean, by the unequal and dissimilar chelipeds (
Fig. 3
) (vs chelipeds subequal in size and similar in shape); rather smooth pleura (
Fig. 2E
